---
// Banner "Agenda próximamente" con captura de email
---

<section id="agenda" class="py-20 md:py-28 bg-surface bg-topo">
  <div class="max-w-[1280px] mx-auto px-5 md:px-16">
    <div class="bg-primary text-on-primary rounded-2xl overflow-hidden relative shadow-brand">
      <div class="absolute inset-0 opacity-15 pointer-events-none">
        <span class="material-symbols-outlined text-[420px] absolute -right-12 -bottom-20 leading-none">event_upcoming</span>
      </div>

      <div class="relative grid grid-cols-1 lg:grid-cols-12 gap-8 p-8 md:p-12 lg:p-16 items-center">
        <div class="lg:col-span-7">
          <span class="inline-flex items-center gap-2 bg-tertiary-fixed text-on-tertiary-fixed font-label text-xs font-semibold uppercase tracking-widest px-4 py-1.5 rounded-full mb-5">
            <span class="material-symbols-outlined text-base">schedule</span>
            Próximamente
          </span>
          <h2 class="font-headline text-3xl md:text-5xl uppercase leading-tight mb-4">
            Agenda en construcción
          </h2>
          <p class="text-lg text-on-primary/90 mb-2 max-w-xl">
            Estamos confirmando con los conferencistas internacionales y panelistas las sesiones definitivas del seminario.
          </p>
          <p class="text-base text-on-primary/75 max-w-xl">
            Déjanos tu correo y te avisamos en cuanto publiquemos la programación oficial.
          </p>
        </div>

        <div class="lg:col-span-5">
          <form
            action="https://formspree.io/f/agenda-seminario"
            method="POST"
            class="bg-surface-container-lowest rounded-xl p-6 text-on-surface"
          >
            <label for="agenda-email" class="block font-label text-xs font-semibold uppercase text-primary mb-2">
              Notificarme cuando esté lista
            </label>
            <div class="flex flex-col sm:flex-row gap-2">
              <input
                id="agenda-email"
                name="email"
                type="email"
                required
                placeholder="tu@correo.com"
                class="flex-1 px-4 py-3 rounded-md border border-outline-variant bg-surface-container-lowest text-on-surface focus:outline-none focus:border-primary focus:ring-2 focus:ring-primary/20 text-sm"
              />
              <input type="hidden" name="_subject" value="Aviso agenda seminario carreteras" />
              <button
                type="submit"
                class="inline-flex items-center justify-center px-5 py-3 bg-primary text-on-primary rounded-md font-label text-sm font-semibold uppercase hover:bg-primary-container transition-colors whitespace-nowrap"
              >
                Avísame
                <span class="material-symbols-outlined ml-2 text-base">notifications_active</span>
              </button>
            </div>
            <p class="text-[11px] text-on-surface-variant mt-3">
              Solo te escribiremos para anunciarte la agenda. No spam.
            </p>
          </form>
        </div>
      </div>
    </div>
  </div>
</section>
